oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Bluff Park
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: parks; Bluff Park;
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: A couple stands, looking out toward the Mississippi River, with the Cossitt Library and US Custom House in the background. Bluff Park is the current site of a parking garage and a firehouse.
